    <p>
      Conan is a macOS-native desktop application that observes and visualizes
      Claude Code. It does not replace Claude Code or run any model itself; you
      run Claude Code yourself and Conan adds an observability layer around it.
      Conan runs locally on your Mac and reads Claude Code's local session data.
    </p>
